<p>
  You'll also have to configure your Twilio SMS endpoints to connect to your application.
</p>
  <a href="https://ibb.co/bCv1Lo"><img src="https://preview.ibb.co/jeSsRT/Screen_Shot_2018_05_21_at_5_51_07_PM.png" alt="Screen_Shot_2018_05_21_at_5_51_07_PM" border="0"></a>
<p>
  If the application is hosted locally, you'll need to set up tunneling so the application
  can be reached from the web.  I use Ngrok, but hosting on Heroku could work as well. 
</p>
